OL,3,CUniversity student denies murdering
OL,4,Chis housemate
OL,6,FA student has denied murdering his
OL,7,Fhousemate in Bristol earlier this year.
OL,9,FJamie Collins, from Swansea, was found
OL,10,Fdead in his house in Bristol in April.
OL,12,FZack Coughlan, 23, appeared before the
OL,13,Fcity's crown court charged with
OL,14,Fmurdering Jamie Collins, aged 21, on 8
OL,15,FApril.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
