PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782125277
OL,3,CUniversity student denies murdering
OL,4,Chis housemate
OL,6,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,7,Fgarden at the rear of the property
OL,8,Fwhere they lived in a house share in
OL,9,FCleve Road, Filton, South
OL,10,FGloucestershire, in the early hours of
OL,11,F9 April.
OL,13,FMr Collins, from Swansea, who studied
OL,14,Frobotics at the University of the West
OL,15,Fof England, was found with significant
OL,16,Finjuries and pronounced dead at the
OL,17,Fscene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
