CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782125277
OL,3,CUniversity student denies murdering
OL,4,Chis housemate
OL,6,FOn Friday 19 June, Coughlan was asked
OL,7,Fto enter a plea to the charge that he
OL,8,Fmurdered Mr Collins and he replied
OL,9,F"not guilty".
OL,11,FJudge Julian Lambert told the court
OL,12,Fthe trial is expected to start on 12
OL,13,FOctober. The court heard the trial is
OL,14,Fexpected to last between two to three
OL,15,Fweeks.
OL,17,FAdam Vaitilingam KC appeared for the
OL,18,Fprosecution, while Edd Hetherington
OL,19,Frepresented Coughlan.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
