PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782125277
OL,3,CUniversity student denies murdering
OL,4,Chis housemate
OL,6,FCoughlan was remanded into custody
OL,7,Fahead of his next appearance at court
OL,8,Fon 25 September.
OL,10,FThe family of Mr Collins previously
OL,11,Fpaid tribute to him in a statement
OL,12,Freleased through Avon and Somerset
OL,13,FPolice.
OL,15,F"Our Jamie was a bright, kind, gentle
OL,16,Fand unassuming young man with his
OL,17,Fwhole life ahead of him," they said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
