PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782125277
OL,3,CUniversity student denies murdering
OL,4,Chis housemate
OL,6,F"He was looking forward to finishing
OL,7,Fhis uni journey and planning to come
OL,8,Fhome to us in Swansea in just a few
OL,9,Fweeks' time.
OL,11,F"We know he was heading for a hugely
OL,12,Fsuccessful future following his
OL,13,Fengineering and robotics degree."
OL,15,FThe University of the West of England
OL,16,F(UWE Bristol) also described being
OL,17,F"deeply shocked" by his death.
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@PO]
