CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1782125277
OL,3,CUniversity student denies murdering
OL,4,Chis housemate
OL,6,F"As well as studying robotics, Jamie
OL,7,Fwas also an active member of student
OL,8,Fsocieties at UWE Bristol," a
OL,9,Fspokesperson said.
OL,11,F"The university will support students
OL,12,Fwho studied with Jamie and staff
OL,13,Fdirectly affected by his death."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/6
